quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  36,28,"Ne shikhweshiakhwo khubandu be imbeli wuwe omukanda kweliyie okhurula mwikulu, ne shikhwali beshia tawe."
  36,29,"Lwali butswa oluyoka lulala, lola, bali bamalile okhusuma."
  36,30,""Abaane, ebeelelela abandu banje. Omurumwa yesiyesi shiyabetselanga tawe okhula bamubayile.""
  36,31,"Koo, shibalolangakhwo nemikanda chinga chakhwasishia imbeli wabu? Abo toto shibali babakalushila tawe."
  36,32,"Ne toto boosi balikhung’asibwa barerwe imbeli wefu."
  36,33,"Ne eshimanyisio khubo ni liloba [eliumu] liafwa, khulilamusinjia mana khuchesemwo imele yabaliitsanga."
  36,34,"Ne nikhukasiamwo emikunda chia tsitende nende tsizabibu, ne nikhukasiamwo tsisebele."
  36,35,"Kho balie khubiamo bie, nende aka emikhono chiabu chilakholele tawe. Koo, shibakhupanga orio tawe!"
  36,36,"Obutswenufu nibwa Nyasaye waloonga eshisatsa neshikhasi bioosi khubimelanga mwiloba, nende enywe abeene, nende ebiabalamanyile tawe."
  36,37,"Ne eshilo neshimanyisio shindi khubo, olwa khurusinjiamwo eshiteere, ne lola, baba mushiilima."
  36,38,"Ne eliuba lichendanga khushichelo shalio. Esho nisho eshichelo shia Nyasaye Owamaani, Omumanyi muno."
  36,39,"Ne Omwesi khwakurereraho ameshelo okhula kukalukhe kube shingala likhamari liumile."
  36,40,"Eliuba shiniliula khumwesi nohomba eshilo okhubura eshitere tawe, nabo bioosi bibotokhananga khutsinjila tsiabio."